manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Not just Factory Replacements FACT-UP Factory Upgrade Lug Nuts by DPAccessories Elevate your wheels with FACT-UP lug nuts: Beyond mere replacements, they're a superior upgrade! Made from hardened steel with durable chrome and black plated finishes. Precision-engineered for an unmatched fit. Trust in the expertise of the industry's leading wheel accessory brand since 2008.

Durable Factory Style Replacements Engineered as Direct Replacements for your Ram 1500 Designed for your 19-24 Ram 1500 factory aluminum wheels. Direct OEM replacements mirror the hex size, seat width & style for a safe fit with an improved look. Drive with confidence and style; choose the upgrade, not just a replacement.

Ditch those capped lugs and get the look you want! Thin cap can fail, leaving you stranded OEM Ram 1500 lug nuts have a thin tin cap that can be damaged from regular use. Wheel removal becomes a daunting challenge if this cap strips or fails, especially in emergencies. Upgrading to a solid lug nut gives you peace of mind. Add your personal style with durable finishes The dull silver factory lug nuts can diminish the shine of polished or chrome wheels and stand out in the wrong way on dark wheel finishes. Upgrade to solid chrome or black plated lug nuts for a refined look and add that personal touch.

Look us up, we're on the map! Your Trusted Choice for Lug Nuts Since 2008 DPAccessories has been the source for premium lug nuts, operating proudly from Kent, Washington. Our in-house design, testing, and packaging ensure quality and consistency that you can depend on. When you choose us, you're purchasing from a team that has made the decision to focus on what we know best. We're nuts about lug nuts! From all of us at Driven Products, thank you for your continued support.

I have a Ram 1500 Classic that is 5-lug, not 6-lug. Are these lug nuts still a good fit? Yes! The OEM lug nut is the same for 2019-2023 Ram 1500 Classic models, you'll just have 4 spare lug nuts if you purchase this set. You can also change to the "2012-2018 Factory Wheel" option at the top of this page for a 5-lug kit of these lug nuts. Are these lug nuts the same length as the OEM lug nuts? They look taller. Good eye! At 1.65" they are about 1/8" taller than stock. We do this to match the internal depth on the factory capped lug nuts. They will stick out of the wheel a little more than stock, but we think they look great. Is the black finish matte black? Gloss black? Does the chrome rust? We call our black plating a satin finish, right in the middle of matte and gloss. Black and chrome platings have been upgraded to pass extended corrosion tests and will look great for years with only a little cleaning when they get dirty. Will these fit ALL 2019-2024 Ram 1500 aluminum wheels? What about factory steel wheels with a center cap? These lug nuts are designed to directly replace OEM part# 6509422AA. If that's the lug nut you have now, these will work! If your lug nuts hold on a wheel cover or if there is a cap that covers your lug nuts these are not compatible. Can I use an impact wrench with these lug nuts? How much torque can they take? Impact wrenches are no problem for hardened steel and our plating! Just don't over-do it, this isn't Nascar. Too much torque is not better, so use a torque wrench to tighten to the torque spec recommended in your Owner's manual.
